overview: It's time for the stagecoach race to win the mail contract and the only entries are Reden and Farrell. Reden's men kidnap Farrell's daughter and then force him to withdraw. Wally rescues Ruth, buys out Farrel, and enters the race himself. But Reden has his men planted along the course to make sure Wally doesn't win.
tagline: Here they come! Redmen and whitemen in a true blue tale of the wild and wooly west!
title: Red Fork Range
